column1: You're a DoorDash analyst! DoorDash Marketing Team is interested in rolling out coupons and promotions across the country and they need your expertise! You will explore delivery times and cuisine trends in a number of major cities in the U.S. to aid the marketing team in developing a promotional plan for its most valued customers.

For this task, you'll engage the following skills:

(1) Prepare the data by transforming it.
(2) Summarize each market region by creating a PivotTable.
(3) Summarize the orders by category by creating a PivotTable.
(4) LevelUP by creating a PivotTable that summarizes delivery times by cuisine.
